title: I Want To Live Out My Fantasies

description:
I have been married for two years. I love my wife with everything inside of me and I want to spend the rest of my life with her. She is an amazing mother and wife. We have a great sex life. My problem is that I want more. I want to be in an open relationship or at least be a swinging couple.
